00:06:42.566 --> 00:06:47.566
and we are approaching negative infinity.

00:06:48.088 --> 00:06:50.233
We are approaching negative infinity.

00:06:50.233 --> 00:06:52.766
That's what the graph of
tangent of theta looks

00:06:52.766 --> 00:06:57.366
just over this section
of, I guess we could say

00:06:57.366 --> 00:06:59.833
the theta axis, but then
we could keep going.

00:06:59.833 --> 00:07:02.300
Then we could keep going because

